<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> | OAT LIMITED</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About OAT LIMITED</h1>
        <p>Building Africa's future with excellence and innovation</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="about-text">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2015, OAT LIMITED began with a vision to transform Africa's construction landscape through innovative engineering solutions and sustainable building practices.</p>
            <p>What started as a small team of passionate engineers and architects has grown into a leading construction and engineering firm serving clients across the continent and beyond.</p>
            
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To deliver cutting-edge infrastructure solutions that contribute to Africa's urban development while maintaining the highest standards of quality, sustainability, and innovation.</p>
            
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul class="values-list">
              <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We commit to the highest standards in everything we do.</li>
              <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We constantly seek better, smarter solutions to construction challenges.</li>
              <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We design with the future in mind, minimizing environmental impact.</li>
              <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We maintain transparency and honesty in all our dealings.</li>
              <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> We believe in the power of teamwork and partnerships.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="about-image" style="background-image: url('/api/placeholder/500/400'); background-size: cover;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Leadership Team</h2>
        <div class="team-grid">
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image" style="background-image: url('/api/placeholder/300/300'); background-size: cover;"></div>
            <h3>Oluwaseun Adeyemi</h3>
            <p class="member-title">Founder & CEO</p>
            <p>With over 20 years of experience in civil engineering and construction management, Oluwaseun leads our company with vision and expertise.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image" style="background-image: url('/api/placeholder/300/300'); background-size: cover;"></div>
            <h3>Taiwo Oluwatosin</h3>
            <p class="member-title">Chief Operations Officer</p>
            <p>Taiwo oversees all operational aspects of our projects, ensuring efficient execution and quality delivery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image" style="background-image: url('/api/placeholder/300/300'); background-size: cover;"></div>
            <h3>Amara Nwachukwu</h3>
            <p class="member-title">Head of Engineering</p>
            <p>A structural engineering expert, Amara leads our engineering team in developing innovative solutions for complex projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="certifications">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Certifications & Partnerships</h2>
        <div class="cert-grid">
          <div class="cert-item">
            <i class="fas fa-certificate"></i>
            <h4>ISO 9001:2015</h4>
            <p>Quality Management Systems</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
            <h4>LEED Accredited</h4>
            <p>Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            <h4>ISO 45001</h4>
            <p>Occupational Health and Safety</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
            <h4>African Construction Partnership</h4>
            <p>Continental Building Standards</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>